commit_message:
Add test to check that it is not be possible to disable current project.

1) Go to Identity -> Projects;
1) Switch project to 'demo';
2) Open 'Edit Project' and check that:
    - Project is enabled and checkbox is marked;
    - Checkbox is disabled;
    - Text 'You cannot disable your current project' present on page.

Implements blueprint: horizon-integration-tests-coverage
